for FreeBSD target systems:
copy 
 patch-erts_emulator_hipe_hipe__bif0.c
 patch-lib_crypto_c_src_crypto__drv.c
 patch-lib_crypto_src_crypto.erl
to $PORTSROOT/lang/erlang/files before building the port

for all other target systems: 
apply 
  patch-lib_crypto_c__src_crypto__drv.c
  patch-lib_crypto_src_crypto.erl
in the otp_src_R13B01 directory before building

